  "description": [
    "Mrs Schuyler Says By JOSEJHINE SCHUYLER Calvin Service The European Jitters Throwing Ethiopia to the Ital ians for the purpose of avoiding another European conflict has not helped Europes situation a jot The present civil war in Spain is very liable to bring the long ex pected crisis to a head It is re ported that Soviet Russia and the workers in France are helping the Spanish Loyalists which ironic ally enough are the Reds of Anda lusia and it is proved beyond doubt that Fascist Italy sent bombing planes to Morocco to help the Spanish Rebels which fan tastically enough are the Fas cists in this colony of Spain and Germany is also doing her bit to help Fascism there This is the beginning apparently of a gigan tis struggle to the death between Communism and Fascism in Eu rope Industrialism in Chains Fascism has been called Capi talism with guns but I prefer to call it industrialism in chains Capitalism is but one phase of in dustrialism the first stage of the machine method of production Capitalism little more than a hun dred years old has already reached its limitations Fascism is an ef fort to keep industrialism"
  ],
